&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>O wise one you know your limitations, &lt;br>
You know your helplessness, &lt;br>
You know your boundary, &lt;br>
You know you have a desire &lt;br>
To live in boundless space &lt;br>
and in a timeless time &lt;br>
A desire to expand your Relationship, &lt;br>
business and influence Infinitely &lt;br>
A desire to live and enjoy &lt;br>
present and future without dropping &lt;br>
your past good moments.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>